commit.title: [kernel] Handle opaque bodies and constraints together.
commit.message:
[kernel] Handle opaque bodies and constraints together.

We simplify the opaque fetching API as to return a body and their
constraints together.

This IMHO makes sense as the underlying future has them together and
thus the whole entity is forced no matter what we'd like to retrieve.

Depends on #8787 but could be made independent.
